[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大乘集菩薩學論卷第二",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078a22_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "法稱菩薩造",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏銀青光祿大夫",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試光祿卿普明慈覺傳梵大師賜紫沙門臣法護等奉　詔譯2集布施學品第一之二論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078a29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故知自力所集，隨其行相於一善道亦應守護。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《地藏十論經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是十善業道佛所證果，若不真實守護一善業道，乃至臨命終時而自稱言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『我是真實行大乘者，我求阿耨多羅三藐三菩提者。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b04_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』當知是人是極虛詐、是大妄語，對十方界佛世尊前誑惑世間，說空斷見誘誑愚癡，身壞命終墮諸惡趣。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至臨命終時，能須臾說集諸善品，亦應修作。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《藥師琉璃光經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若見大心眾生，如聞菩薩難行苦行及妙勝智，乃至入解、發大勇猛荷負重擔、捄護眾生盡諸苦本，禮拜供養、說罪及隨喜福、勸請諸佛住世說法，乃至迴向菩提，為善知識勸請說法或樂自說，當知是名為示道者。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b13_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如《文殊師利莊嚴佛剎功德經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是妙吉祥往昔生時，本行因緣發菩提心，亦如是發，如彼所說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至最初遠離輪迴邊際，利益眾生行如是行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b16_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我於尊所發菩提心，現前勸請令諸世間脫貧窮報忿心恨心慳貪嫉妬，我得菩提時悉不現起，乃至常修梵行脫諸罪欲。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b19_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於佛隨學清淨尸羅，愛樂尊重於大菩提，不疾取證，我處後際，於諸眾生一相無異。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b21_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時十方界未聞我名無量不思議剎土悉皆嚴淨，由身語意業清淨故，於諸所作悉亦清淨。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又一切時堅持淨戒，盡生死際無諸過惡。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b24_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又《阿閦如來本願授決經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b25_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼阿閦如來往昔為菩薩時，作如是說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b25_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『若我生生世世不出家者，是則虛誑一切諸佛如來。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b27_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是菩薩於阿閦如來亦應隨學。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078b28_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸菩薩摩訶薩生生出家，或諸如來出世或不出世畢竟捨家出家，亦如是學。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c01_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若謂菩薩捨家出家是為最上，乃至男女眷屬不生愛著，如我生時無諸過失。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如上所說，且止斯事。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若說施戒罪相同等，及於罪相相應等事，應自棄捨。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若別別行相亦非無罪，於別行相然不攝故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩於諸眾生所有未來一切苦惱令得解脫、一切妙樂令其增長，若身語意不勤精進方便純熟，於緣合集不樂勸化，或散滅處亦不尋求，多分煩惱少分煩惱不起對治，於大義利及少義利或非義利不生損益，剎那俱捨，此說是罪。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "略說無罪，謂自力能於境界事都無果報。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或執如是於學表相體性是罪。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若自力能境界相應罪處無有，同說罪等於相解脫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩學於平等身廣太無量劫後際說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次略說菩薩此二種罪，如其成辦相應非相應、可作不可作都無揀擇，捨故是罪。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂言畢竟超出尋伺，如旃陀羅奴等謬解義故是罪。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c18_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼復云何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c18_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "《深心教誡經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c19_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如慈氏因中四種辯才即諸佛語。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者擇有義利揀非義利、二者擇此正法揀彼非法、三者破遣煩惱非增長煩惱、四者樂見涅盤功德不樂見輪迴功德，是名四種。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c23_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以要言之，若爾云何慈氏因中說是四種辯才？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c24_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂信善男子善女人生諸佛想、作議論想，聞善法故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c25_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若慈氏有諸善說即諸佛語故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c26_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於此慈氏辯才而生誹謗，非諸佛語起不尊重，是惡人輩即是誹謗諸佛所說辯才，由毀減善法招罪業報墮諸惡趣。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0078c29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a01_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次修習善巧發起愛樂，此行門中集學最勝作用，應當修學，希大果故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a02_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《寂靜決定神變經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a03_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩於殑伽沙數等諸佛，是諸佛所有殑伽沙數佛剎，復於如是殑伽沙數劫，以自在王摩尼寶滿中持用布施。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a06_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸菩薩於如是法相聞已，一心思惟我當修學。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a07_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "比前無學所有福報，未若施此樂欲學地菩薩，其福甚多。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩雖見此功德，未言如其修習等。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復如彼說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "假使教化三千大千世界微塵等眾生，一一眾生得閻浮王。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a11_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若以諸音聲讚歎受持讀誦如說修行大乘經者，於一日夜斷割身肉指爪，乃至命終一心奉行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "緣是菩薩布施心無怯弱、不驚不怖不畏，畢竟一心發親近想，無悔無疑亦無分別，於此最上正法攝受相應，意樂讀誦如說修行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a17_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩心勇猛故，則布施勇猛、持戒勇猛、精進勇猛、禪定勇猛、智慧勇猛、一切三摩地勇猛。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a19_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a19_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩設使於惡人輩，亦復不生瞋心厭心及餘過失。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "文殊師利！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩如釋梵王等無所動。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a21_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今正是時，當一心學，希大果報。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "《月燈三昧經》所說偈云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若於河沙多億劫，供養百億那由佛，清淨信心施餚饍，亦施燈鬘及幡蓋。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a24_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若於正法衰末世，如是佛法欲滅時，於一日夜學是行，比前福報勝於彼。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故一心勤修，如佛經中所說菩薩學義。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《寶雲經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善男子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a28_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於菩薩學堅持淨戒，如是尋伺：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079a29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『若不於菩薩別解脫戒中，我云何能得成證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提耶？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b01_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又何不於如來大乘諸經法中所詮菩薩行所集菩薩學？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我當如是廣大修習。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b03_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我等無知，於此廣說菩薩制止容起惡覺，何非此理，於修習處了無過失。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何修習處？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若於身所有三世受用行清淨捨，護諸眾生令淨增長，受是菩薩戒已，若此菩薩住修習處說是罪相。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b08_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《菩薩別解脫經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b08_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於菩薩道攝受一切眾生令盡苦趣。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼菩薩道攝受安住過俱胝劫，唯一發起安隱之心及親近心。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩發是心者，應知於諸眾生一向攝受多種住處。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如《文殊清淨律》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「時文殊師利語寂音天子言：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『菩薩具足此五無間，速得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為五？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b14_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩深固作意求無上道，發心不墮聲聞緣覺之地，是初無間發心。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b16_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自捨一切所有，於慳悋心而不共住，是二無間。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我應救度一切眾生，於中不起懈退之心，是三無間。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "了一切法非空非有無生無滅，於中不墮諸見，是四無間。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b19_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於諸法智和合一相，如是發心中無所住，由無所住於一切智悉無所得，是五無間。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b21_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂身所受用福報不斷者，於捨護事令淨增長。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如《瑜伽觀想》中說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b23_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼所捨義攝受過失，觀想門中起離貪想，觀捨功德故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b24_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如《月燈三昧經》所說偈云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是不堅身，愚者心所樂。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b25_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何常壽命中，剎那如幻夢。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b26_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "造諸惡業故，罪報常隨逐。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由是無明因，死多墮惡道。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b27_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又如《無量門陀羅尼經》說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何眾生得鬪諍因？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b28_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂計執財利而為根本。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應當棄捨，若離貪愛即得是陀羅尼。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c01_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又《菩薩別解脫經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c01_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c01_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩於一切法極微細分不生他想。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c02_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "怖取著故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」《最上授所問經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c03_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「謂若布施者無諸慳悋，執著者而常守護。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c04_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又布施者為盡貪愛，執著者增長貪愛。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c05_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者無諸遍計，執著者有諸遍計。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者無有恐怖，執著者彼多恐怖。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c07_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者住菩提道，執著者住魔境界。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c07_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者作無盡想，執著者作有盡想。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又布施者得諸妙樂，執著者而常逼迫。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c09_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者捨離煩惱，執著者增長煩惱。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c10_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又布施者得大富饒，執著者得大貧乏。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c11_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者善人事業，執著者惡人情計。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "布施者諸佛稱讚，執著者愚夫稱讚。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至布施者自所生子不起樂著，非如於餘眾生起憐愍故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應知自心說有三種。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c14_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為三？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者菩薩於菩提道正等相應，非邪謬相應。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者菩薩於菩提道起平等心，非高下心。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者菩薩於菩提道無種種行，非有種種行。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c17_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是名三種自心所說。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c18_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」論曰：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c19_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂於自所生子起非善友想，既非善友故非我友。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c20_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若為利益隨佛教勅學負重擔故，於自所生子不生樂著，非如於餘眾生起憐愍故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "應知發是心已，如於我子發生慈愛，則我於一切眾生亦復隨順發生慈愛。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c23_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是深心觀察悟解，我子既無異於一切眾生，則一切眾生皆是我子。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c25_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所有眾生若自若他，乃至居士在家菩薩，於其財利或非攝受眾生，勿應耽著非出離法。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復不應愛樂隨順染欲。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次在家菩薩或有行來乞丐，隨何所須發勇悍心而為給與。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又作是念：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0079c29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我此財利若捨不捨畢竟散滅。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a01_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」云何於捨受時而得無欲？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a01_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂我我所得畢竟忍，於所捨物離胎藏苦，心住正念歡喜愛樂不生隨轉。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a03_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次如是能捨，謂於所捨物及乞丐者應知有四種想。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a04_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂怯弱故，不能純熟善根先所造業；",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a05_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於大乘中心不自在，見取捨故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若我及我所住安忍力，自與善人不起悔惱。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a07_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是修作、如是踊躍、如是精進，圓滿一切眾生所希求故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是在家菩薩於彼乞丐者應作是想。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a09_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或乞丐者返增過失，是菩薩應當善言慰諭。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又乞丐者而不知恩，是菩薩亦復不起慳嫉。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是為無罪。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此世尊為下種諸菩薩，如《菩薩別解脫》中說：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩無有四法。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a13_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等為四？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一者菩薩無不信心；",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "二者菩薩無有慳貪；",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a14_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三者菩薩無有兩舌嫉妬；",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四者菩薩無懈怠心，謂言我不能成證阿耨多羅三藐三菩提果。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a16_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若我有是四法，彼有智者於此了知，便謂邪命諂求非法染法重世財利，是為第一偷食信施。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次舍利子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩如是心勇猛故，乃至頭目手足身體支分、男女眷屬心所愛樂極妙樂事、舍宅國邑一切所有，悉能棄捨。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a21_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」又如《那羅延所問經》云：",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a22_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「若於財寶發是捨心，應知財利不生取著。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然捨未起智故，若於攝受不起捨心，則於非攝受亦常執著。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若隨乞丐者意，於攝受發生智故，則於眷屬亦無取著，最上崇貴亦無取著、受用珍寶亦無取著。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩若於財利不起捨心，乃至極微細分，應知取著。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a27_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次善男子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080a28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而菩薩摩訶薩應當發如是心，謂我此身分於諸眾生尚能棄捨，何況所有外財資具！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又若於眾生所，如其所須悉能施與，謂有來乞丐須手以手須足以足須眼以眼，乃至脂髓血肉及餘身分，隨各施與。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何復名外財資具？",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂若庫藏孳生之物、金銀珍寶勝妙莊嚴、象馬車乘國土宮殿、城邑聚落吏民僮僕、作業士夫男女眷屬。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b06_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸眾生於所有事，彼彼眾生如其所有，我當給與，不生悔惱亦無退屈，不希果報及餘諂詐。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復次我此施者，隨順一切眾生故、悲愍一切眾生故、饒益一切眾生故、攝受一切眾生故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如我攝受眾生，知如是法得菩提故。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以要言之，善男子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b11_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如藥樹根莖枝葉花果皮核，若全若分，隨其取者不生分別。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又復脫諸眾生病苦難時，亦不分別上中下性。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善男子！",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩亦復如是，應知於四大種身生藥樹想，於彼眾生可作饒益，須手以手須足以足，隨其取者如前藥樹不生分別。",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b17_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」大乘集菩薩學論卷第二",
        "from": "T32n1636_002:0080b18_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]